        <text>
            <body><p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324645" xml:id="d1e131047">Stephanus, Dei gracia
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e131049">Eduensis</placeName> episcopus</persName>, et <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324677" xml:id="d1e131053">Gal. <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284217" xml:id="d1e131055">Flavinniasensis</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11791" xml:id="d1e131058">G. <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281589" xml:id="d1e131060">
                                <sic>Altte</sic> Cumbe</orgName>
                        </persName> abbates <lb n="2"/> notum fieri volumus presentibus et futuris
                        quod cumtroversias que inter ecclesiam <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e131067">Fonteneti</orgName> et <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e131071">Ungiaci</orgName> verte<lb n="3" break="no"/>bantur
                        utriusque partis assensu in hunc modum amicabili composicione terminavimus.
                        Composicionem per <lb n="4"/> manum domini <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324654" xml:id="d1e131078">Umberti tunc <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281272" xml:id="d1e131080">Eduensis</orgName> episcopi</persName> factam
                        sicut continetur in carta sigillo ipsius episcopi et abbatis <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e131084">Ungniacen<lb n="5" break="no"/>sis</orgName> signata vel altera simili sigillo episcopi et abbatis de
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e131089">
                            <sic>Funteneto</sic>
                        </orgName> confirmata secundum tenorem instrumenti ipsius inviola<lb n="6" break="no"/>biliter deinceps pars utraque servabit, hoc
                            <sic>ecepto</sic> quod de preteritis expensis vel de fructibus
                        quibuslibet usque ad diem trans<lb n="7" break="no"/>accionis hujus
                        perceptis nulla erit inter eos questio et quicquid a parti alteri adversus
                        alteram super his videbatur <lb n="8"/> de jure repocendum sine ulla
                        retencione sibi invicem remiserunt. <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325030" xml:id="d1e131103">Silvam de <foreign>Leurre</foreign>
                        </placeName> ex equo parcientur ad arbitri<lb n="9" break="no"/>um abbatis
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283145" xml:id="d1e131111">Longi Vuadi</orgName>
                        et fratris <persName key="d1e11797" xml:id="d1e131114">Roberti de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324328" xml:id="d1e131116">Annaio</placeName>
                        </persName>, quibus erit plena potestas dividere eam secundum quod congruum
                            <lb n="10"/> sibi videbitur utriusque partis commoditate servata. Si
                        inter eosdem duos de divisione minus convenerit <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284217" xml:id="d1e131121">Flavi<lb n="11" break="no"/>gniacensis</orgName> et de monasterio <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283938" xml:id="d1e131126">Sancti Johannis</orgName> abbates eandem silvam
                        dividant inter eos. Porro pro medietate silve <lb n="12"/> illius <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e131132">
                            <sic>Unniacences</sic>
                        </orgName> annuatim solvent monasterio <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e131136">Fonteneti</orgName> censum sex denariorum in pascuis
                        territorii <lb n="13"/> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324449" xml:id="d1e131141">Estormer</placeName> et <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324335" xml:id="d1e131144">Noville Montis</placeName>
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e131146">Ungniacenses</orgName>
                        sexaginta animalia et non amplius habere poterunt. Fratres autem <lb n="14"/>
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e131151">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        animalia sua et in suis et in pascuis de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324988" xml:id="d1e131154">Pretenerio</placeName> ducent sine contradiccione.
                        Terram de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324446" xml:id="d1e131157">Ampille</placeName> fra<lb n="15" break="no"/>tres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e131162">Ungiacensis</orgName> ecclesie
                        in omni pace deinceps retinebunt. Similiter de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325172" xml:id="d1e131166">prato <sic>Teolbaudi</sic>
                            Berardi</placeName> omnis est quere<lb n="16" break="no"/>la <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e131174">Fontenetensium</orgName> sopita.
                        Et quia fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e131177">Ungiacen<subst>
                                <del>c</del>
                                <add>s</add>
                            </subst>es</orgName> edificia sua in territorio de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325288" xml:id="d1e131186">Fromasio</placeName> mutaverunt
                            <lb n="17"/> secundum cantitatem illius loci ubi priora edificia fuerant
                        in illo loco ubi postea edificaverunt cum orto <lb n="18"/> illo adviridario
                        que ibi prius abuerant ex composicione eadem tantundem spacii eis im <lb n="19"/> pace remanebit. Quod superfuerit in clausura grangie per medium
                        dividetur et medietatem <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324372" xml:id="d1e131196">Ungiacenses</placeName>
                        <lb n="20"/> im pace similiter habebunt, pro altera medietate comutacionem
                        dabunt illis de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e131200">Fonteneto</orgName> ubi abbas <lb n="21"/>
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283145" xml:id="d1e131204">Longi Vadi</orgName> et
                        frater <persName key="d1e11797" xml:id="d1e131208">Robertus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324328" xml:id="d1e131210">Aennaio</placeName>
                        </persName> constituerint secundum arbitrium suum vel si inter eos non
                        convenerit <lb n="22"/>
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284217" xml:id="d1e131214">Flavigniacensis</orgName>
                        et de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283938" xml:id="d1e131217">Monasterio Sancti
                            Johannis</orgName> abbatis preceperint, et ipsi diviserint utrique
                            recipient.<lb n="23"/> Si forte animalia<note>
                            <p rend="footnote text">||-lia… <hi rend="italic">début de B</hi>.</p>
                        </note> utriuslibet partis morbida esse constiterit, in teritorium partis
                        alterius quamdiu morbi<lb n="24" break="no"/>da fuerint ducere <choice>
                            <sic corresp="#A">nom</sic>
                            <corr>non</corr>
                        </choice> poterit.</p>
                    <p>Actum <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#98064" xml:id="d1e131241">Lugduni</placeName>,
                        anno ab incarnacione Domini <num>m° c° <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">octogesimo</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">lxxx°</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </num>, astan<lb n="25" break="no"/>tibus et astestantibus <persName key="d1e11807" xml:id="d1e131254">D. abbate <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#324497" xml:id="d1e131256">Sancte <app>
                                    <lem wit="#A">
                                        <sic>Marguarite</sic>
                                    </lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#B">Margarite</rdg>
                                </app>
                            </orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11813" xml:id="d1e131265">H. abbate <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284111" xml:id="d1e131267">Benedicionis Dei</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11819" xml:id="d1e131271">P. preposito
                                <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281272" xml:id="d1e131273">Eduensi</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11825" xml:id="d1e131276">G. <lb n="26"/>
                            archidiacono <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#321577" xml:id="d1e131280">
                                <app>
                                    <lem wit="#A">
                                        <sic>Cabilonensu</sic>
                                    </lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#B">Cabilonensi</rdg>
                                </app>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11831" xml:id="d1e131288">G. priore
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324403" xml:id="d1e131290">Barri</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11837" xml:id="d1e131293">G. de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324977" xml:id="d1e131295">
                                <foreign>Perrol</foreign>
                            </placeName> archidiacono <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e131299">Eduensi</placeName>
                        </persName>.</p>
                
            </body>
